sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Mobile Client
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as SQLite / postgres
    participant Drone as Autopilot Core (PX4)

    User->>API: POST /api/v1/orders (lat, lon, weight)
    API->>DB: Record new mission as "Pending"
    API->>API: Calculate route & NPNT clearance
    API->>User: Return mission ID & clearance code
    API->>Drone: Upload Waypoints via MAVLink
    Drone->>Drone: Run preflight self-checks
    Drone->>API: Post telemetry: Arming & Takeoff
    Note over Drone: Cruise and autonomous navigation
    Drone->>Drone: Land & Release Payload
    Drone->>Drone: RTL (Return-to-Launch)
    Drone->>API: Post telemetry: Landed & Disarmed
    API->>DB: Update mission status to "Completed"
